description: This file defines a repository interface for FeedbackEntity objects in a Spring Data JPA context. It extends JpaRepository and provides custom query methods for retrieving feedback based on passenger and facility identifiers.

classes.name: FeedbackRepository
classes.description: Repository interface for FeedbackEntity, extending JpaRepository to provide CRUD operations and custom query methods.

methods.name: findByPassengerIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc
methods.description: Retrieves a list of FeedbackEntity objects associated with a specific passenger, ordered by creation date descending.

methods.name: findByFacilityIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc
methods.description: Retrieves a list of FeedbackEntity objects associated with a specific facility, ordered by creation date descending.
